<H1> 300 B.C.    Olympiad 120.1</H1>
<BR> Consuls: M. Valerius M.f. <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/c/corvus.html#1">Corvus</A> (V), Q. Appuleius <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/p/pansa.html#1">Pansa</A> 
<BR>   Athenian <A CLASS="help" HREF="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Archon_of_Athens">archon</A>: Hegemachus
<BR> <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/o/olympic.html#1">Olympic</A> victor in the <A CLASS="help" HREF="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stadion_%28running_race%29">stadion</A> race: <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/p/pythagoras.html#3">Pythagoras</A> of <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/m/magnesia.html#1">Magnesia-on-Maeander.</A> 
